et | first3 = H. | title = Locomotion of ''Spirilla'' | journal = [[Biophysical Journal]] | volume = 12 | issue = 11 | pages = 1549\u20131561 | date = November 1972 | issn = 1542-0086 | doi = 10.1016/S0006-3495(72)86181-2 | pmid = 4642227 | pmc = 1484193 | bibcode=1972BpJ....12.1549C}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Dawkins\">{{cite news | last = Dawkins | first = Richard | authorlink = Richard Dawkins | title = Why Don't Animals Have Wheels? | work = [[The Sunday Times|Sunday Times]] | date = November 24, 1996 | url = http://www.simonyi.ox.ac.uk/dawkins/WorldOfDawkins-archive/Dawkins/Work/Articles/1996-11-24wheels.shtml |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070221073440/http://www.simonyi.ox.ac.uk/dawkins/WorldOfDawkins-archive/Dawkins/Work/Articles/1996-11-24wheels.shtml |archivedate = February 21, 2007}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"de_Plancy_1825\">{{cite book|last1=de Plancy|first1=Jacques-Albin-Simon Collin|authorlink=Jacques Collin de Plancy|language=French|title=Dictionnaire Infernal|date=1825|publisher=P. Mongie a\u00een\u00e9|page=[https://archive.org/details/dictionnaireinf03plangoog/page/n513 478]|url=https://archive.org/details/dictionnaireinf03plangoog|accessdate=12 September 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"de_Plancy_1863\">{{cite book|last1=de Plancy|first1=Jacques-Albin-Simon Collin|authorlink=Jacques Collin de Plancy|language=French|title=Dictionnaire Infernal|date=1863|editor=Henri Plon|page=123|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=REN0H5OXxjYC|accessdate=12 September 2016|isbn=978-2-05-101277-5}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Donat\">{{Cite web|title=Robot Feet vs. Wheels: The Conundrum|first1=Wolfram|last1=Donat|first2=Gretchen|last2=Giles|date=December 5, 2014|website=Makezine.com|url=http://makezine.com/2014/12/05/robot-feet-vs-wheels-the-conundrum/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327214528/http://makezine.com/2014/12/05/robot-feet-vs-wheels-the-conundrum/|archivedate=March 27, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Crofts\">{{Cite web | last = Crofts