oks?id=z_xyfJDCNAcC&printsec=frontcover&pg=PA1#v=onepage&q&f=false |publisher=Elsevier |pages=1, 31 |isbn=978-0-08-087572-9 |via=Google Books }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"kimura\">{{cite journal | last1 = Kimura | first1 = Motoo |title=The Neutral Theory of Molecular Evolution: A Review of Recent Evidence | journal=Japanese Journal of Genetics |volume=66 |issue=4 |pages=367\u2013386 |year=1991 |pmid=1954033 |doi=10.1266/jjg.66.367|doi-access=free }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=kristensen>{{cite journal|last1=Kristensen|first1=J. Hilleberg|title=Structure and Function of Crystalline Styles of Bivalves|journal=Ophelia|date=August 1972|volume=10|pages=91\u2013108|doi=10.1080/00785326.1972.10430106}}{{subscription required|s}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Krus\">{{cite web | last = Kruszelnicki | first = Karl S. | title = Real Wheel Animals\u2014Part Two | work = Great Moments in Science | publisher = ABC Science | date = August 9, 1999 | url = http://www.abc.net.au/science/articles/1999/08/09/42510.htm?site=science/greatmomentsinscience | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161001195024/http://www.abc.net.au/science/articles/1999/08/09/42510.htm?site=science%2Fgreatmomentsinscience | archivedate = October 1, 2016 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LaBarbera\">{{cite journal | last = LaBarbera | first = Michael | title = Why the Wheels Won't Go | journal = The American Naturalist | volume = 121 | issue = 3 | pages = 395\u2013408 |date=March 1983 | jstor = 2461157 | doi = 10.1086/284068 }}{{subscription required|s}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"lienhard\">{{cite episode | title = A Man with Wheels? | url = http://www.uh.edu/engines/epi406.htm | series = The Engines of Our Ingenuity | credits = Lienhard, John H. | network = [[National Public Radio]] | station = [[KUHF]]-FM | number = 406 | publisher = University of Houston | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160824161302/http://www.uh.edu/engines/epi406.htm | archivedate = August 24, 2016 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n\n<ref nam